Safety and Efficacy of the BNT162b2 mRNA #COVID19 #Vaccine

Even before the second dose, BNT162b2 was highly efficacious, with a vaccine efficacy of 92.6%, a finding similar to the first-dose efficacy of 92.1% reported for the mRNA-1273 vaccine (Moderna).
